# NSD 六大能力轴一览
# 源: nsd-capability-model.md 内联 mermaid

direction: down

classes: {
  core: { style: { fill: "#dbeafe"; stroke: "#3b82f6" } }
  ops: { style: { fill: "#fef3c7"; stroke: "#f59e0b" } }
}

Core: "NSD 核心" {
  direction: down
  ID: "① 身份与组织\nIdentity & Org" { class: core }
  POL: "② 策略与编排\nPolicy" { class: core }
  NET: "③ 网络编排\nTopology" { class: core }
}
Ops: "运维与观测" {
  direction: down
  OBS: "④ 可观测与审计\nObservability" { class: ops }
  ECO: "⑤ 运营与生态\nEcosystem" { class: ops }
  HA: "⑥ 高可用与扩展\nReliability" { class: ops }
}

Core.ID -> Core.POL
Core.POL -> Core.NET
Core.NET -> Ops.OBS
Ops.OBS -> Ops.ECO
Core.ID -> Ops.ECO
Core.POL -> Ops.OBS
Core.ID -> Ops.HA
Ops.HA -> Core.NET
